&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Economics, Finance, Engineering, Mathematics, or a similar quantitative field with a record of strong academic performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct experience in Fraud Strategy and Analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in SQL and Python.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience helping scale a business in a fast-pac

